data.meta_description: The Casper Tribune-Herald Monday, April 14, 1941 Page 4  Max Wimber, 16, Claimed In Denver  Stricken by illness only two weeks ago, Max Wimber, 16, son of Mr. and Mrs. I. C. Wimber, 140 East Midwest Ave., died Saturday night in a Denver hospital.  He was removed there during his illness.  Funeral services will be...
